reviews.text:
Didn't plan on stopping there, but was pleasantly surprised.
Had the Mexican Burger, ground steak hand formed, with green pepper, onion, tomato and cilantro.
Perfectly grilled from slight crust to pink center, flipped only once, I demolished it.  It was like the best home-made grilled burger I have ever made.  There's hundreds of ways to ruin a burger, but this place achieved perfection.
The traditional Mexican items were also great according to my kids.
Great selection of some Mexican classics. The price was pretty great! Wide variety of tequilas! Loved the food and the dessert! Overall very satisfied with the cozy atmosphere and service
Best red sauce for chips. My son loves the orange sauce and my parents love the green, you have to ask for it. Something for everyone. Good tacos. Staple in Glen Ellyn for many, many years.

Friendly restaurant with extensive, creative and authentic menu. They will also custom make a dish to fit your dietary needs. Fantastic margaritas...best of all the staff and owners are super people.  Have been coming here regularly for years.

Not fancy, but if you want a simple American-Mexican food with fairly standard fair for a good price, this is your place. Great for families with little kids.  If you want high end or very traditional Mexican look elsewhere. My kids love this place.

Was very impressed! Good food, great for sharing. Highly suggest getting three or four items and sharing. Our friends like the yogurt drinks. 
Bonus, they have a great yard that our kids could all run around in and we can watch them form the tables.
A good place for Asian foods.

The best Indian food that I've had in all of east Africa.  Service was friendly and fast! The waiters were very quick to refill drinks.  Dinner in most other restaurants took about 2.5hrs. As a party of four here, we were served within 20 minutes and were done within 1hr 30.  We ended up eating here twice because it was so good.
Best restaurant in the world. I’m drooling now just thinking about it. Fast service, good food, friendly staff.

Steady quality makes Almanara one of the best dining options in Iguatemi Shopping.
But over the years they have been increasing prices while decreasing the size of several of their dishes, so that currently Almanara has an expensive bill for such an inexpensive, rather simple cuisine that comes in economic portions — but at least quality standards have remained good, and dishes remain as tasty as a decade ago. The high ceilinged saloon creates a very pleasant atmosphere.
Service from the kitchen is fast (since most dishes seem pre made) and waiters are friendly, but it does take a while sometimes to attract the attention of a server and to receive the bill.
Já foi mto bom , hj em dia a comida vem requentada p a mesa.
Amei o Kibe Cru que era o que eu queria conhecer. Excelente atendimento, local agradável e os demais produtos de ótima qualidade.
Ótima qualidade, muito bom atendimento e local agradável, dentro de um dos melhores shopping de Campinas.
Comida maravilhosa e atendimento gentil e simpático.
